responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "706E4D1943F98A373595688B909C98DB", "Many weak individuals have deserted their duties, guards and settlers. We must track them down and make an example of them. No honorable Kaelar abandons the empire. They must be dealt with, be it dead or alive!")
